#: ../../S/slopsucker.rst:5
msgid "slopsucker"
msgstr "slopsucker"

#: ../../S/slopsucker.rst:7
msgid "/slop´suhk·r/, n\\."
msgstr "/slop´suhk·r/, 名詞"

#: ../../S/slopsucker.rst:9
msgid ""
"A lowest-priority task that waits around until everything else has ‘had its "
"fill’ of machine resources. Only when the machine would otherwise be idle is"
" the task allowed to \\`‘suck up the slop’. Also called a hungry puppy or "
"bottom feeder. One common variety of slopsucker hunts for large prime "
"numbers. Compare :ref:`background`\\."
msgstr ""
"他のすべてがマシンのリソースで‘腹を満たした’あとまで待つ、最低優先度のタスク。マシンがそうでなければ遊んでいるときにのみ、そのタスクは\\`‘余りをすする’ことを許される。hungry"
" puppy(腹をすかせた子犬)やbottom "
"feeder(底をあさる者)とも呼ばれる。slopsuckerの一般的な一種は、大きな素数を探す。:ref:`background`\\ と比較せよ。"
